org.spongepowered.api.data.value.mutable

Interface OptionalValue<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of element
    All Superinterfaces:
    BaseValue<Optional<E>>, Value<Optional<E>>

    public interface OptionalValue<E>
extends Value<Optional<E>>
    Represents a Value that can be Optional such that the underlying value may be present or null.
